data.description: Charming bi-level brick home on nearly 1 acre, without the constraints of an HOA. Enter through the foyer, ascend the stairs with brand new plush carpeting to discover a welcoming living room and dining room, creating a seamless flow to the newly modernized renovated kitchen with pristine white cabinetry, quartz countertops, and sleek kitchen island that's designed with adding both style and functionality to the heart of this home. Step out onto to the deck ideal for both relaxing or entertaining. Down the hall you will find 2 bedrooms and a conveniently located full bathroom for your comfort. Make your way downstairs, where you will find 2 additional bedrooms, full bathroom, laundry/utility room with access to outside. In addition, the downstairs features a cozy wood burning fireplace, providing a perfect canvas to make it your own. Step out through the french doors, leading you to an inviting patio where outdoor enjoyment awaits. New LVP flooring in main living areas and bedrooms.
